items.title: Stop benchmarking in the lab: Inclusion Arena shows how LLMs perform in production

items.title: LLMs generate ‘fluent nonsense’ when reasoning outside their training zone
items.description: Chain-of-Thought isn't a plug-and-play solution. For developers, this research offers a blueprint for LLM testing and strategic fine-tuning.
